<font color="#FF0000">LOOKING FOR MY FAMILY</font><br>
<tt>Thu May 29 17:19:53 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
Two tours in Vietnam with the USMC: over 30 years have past and I'm frozen in time!  I need closure and I am unable to achieve it until I can locate &quot;my family&quot; members of my company.  India Company 3/4 Marines; PhuBai...Some family members' names as I remember them:  Duckett, Brown, Stidham, Connelly, Hampton, Gil, Sgt. Shannon, Cpl. Garrett (on the Wall), Baker (on the Wall), ...1965-1966;  1968-1969 Quantri  HeadQuarters Bn 3rd Marines....Stand proud FAMILY ...I love all of you out there.<br>

<p><code>-- Katosan@MSN.COM  (Carter G.L  USMC) </code><p>


